át - 確山夜發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Y%E1%BB%83n-Th%C3%A0nh-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-V%C5%A9-M%E1%BB%A5c-ban-s%C6%B0-x%E1%BB%A9/poem--ICyw9Rn-6nPQW_kzgsUBw">Yển Thành Nhạc Vũ Mục ban sư xứ - 郾城岳武穆班處</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Hy-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/Y%E1%BA%BFt-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-AL0olPLHP54jJBoONVAqww">Yết Nhạc vương từ - 謁岳王祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Hy-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-sOXpvYRwiR8gfmdifTGGJA">Phạm Hy Lượng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
